LinkHome Source Code:

  1.) Directory Index
  2.) Setup & Installation

===============================================================
1.) DIRECTORY INDEX

    src/linkhome  :  Main Web GUI for LinkHome
    src/linkappd  :  Application launcher & manager for LinkHome
    src/debian    :  Debian package configuration
    src/resources :  System startups scripts, linkhome menus, etc


================================================================
2.) SETUP & INSTALLATION

To setup run:

sudo ./setup.sh

Then to start the service run:

./start.sh


Open your browser on your local machine and browse to:

http://localhost:5000/applications

